# Changelog

## [Unreleased]

## [3.0.1] - 2018-06-24

### Changed
* Upgrade `level-packager` from `~3.0.0` to `~4.0.0` (@ralphtheninja)
* Use proper version range for `tape` (@ralphtheninja)
* Tweak copyright years for less maintenance
* Use abstract tests from `level-packager` (@ralphtheninja)

### Added
* Add `standard` (@ralphtheninja)

### Removed
* Remove `.jshintrc` (@ralphtheninja)

## [3.0.0] - 2018-05-23

### Changed
* Upgrade `memdown` to `~3.0.0` (@ralphtheninja)
* Upgrade `level-packager` to `~3.0.0` (@ralphtheninja)

### Added
* Add node 10 to Travis (@ralphtheninja)
* Add `UPGRADING.md` (@ralphtheninja)

### Removed
* Remove node 4 from Travis (@ralphtheninja)

## [2.0.0] - 2018-02-14

### Changed
* Upgrade `memdown` to `~2.0.0` (@ralphtheninja)
* Upgrade `level-packager` to `~2.1.1` (@ralphtheninja)
* README: normalize and tweak style (@ralphtheninja)
* README: add node badge (@ralphtheninja)
* Switch to plain MIT license (@ralphtheninja)

### Added
* Travis: add 9 (@ralphtheninja)

### Removed
* Travis: remove 0.12, 5 and 7 (@ralphtheninja)

## [1.0.2] - 2017-11-28

### Changed
* Update repository url in `package.json` (@juliangruber)

## [1.0.1] - 2017-10-04

### Changed
* Upgrade `memdown` to `~1.4.1` (@ralphtheninja)

## [1.0.0] - 2017-08-17

### Changed
* README: update logo and copyright (@ralphtheninja)
* README: add Greenkeeper badge (@ralphtheninja)
* README: update copyright year to 2017 (@ralphtheninja)
* Upgrade `memdown` to `~1.2.4` (@ralphtheninja)
* Upgrade `level-packager` to `~1.2.1` (@ralphtheninja)

### Added
* Travis: add 4, 5, 6, 7 and 8 (@ralphtheninja)

### Removed
* Travis: remove 0.8 and 0.10 (@ghostbar, @ralphtheninja)

## [0.18.0] - 2013-12-05

### Changed
* Upgrade `memdown` to `~0.6.0` (@rvagg)
* Upgrade `level-packager` to `~0.18.0` (@rvagg)

### Added
* Add Travis (@rvagg)

## 0.17.0 - 2013-10-12

:seedling: Initial release.

